<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.3">
<l>tuṭikoṇ ṇuṇṇiṭaic curikuḻal tuḷaṅkeyiṟ</l>
<l>ḷaṅkoṭi tiṟattāyar</l>
<l>iṭikoḷ veṅkura liṉaviṭai yaṭarttava</l>
<l>ṉiruntanal limayattu</l>
<l>kaṭikoḷ vēṅkaiyiṉ naṟumala ramaḷiyiṉ</l>
<l>maṇiyaṟai micaivēḻam</l>
<l>piṭiyi ṉōṭuvaṇ ṭicaicolat tuyilkoḷum</l>
<l>piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the fair Himalayas where resides the one who controlled</l>
<l rend="indent">the cowherders’ herd of bulls, their angry bellows like thunder,</l>
<l>For the sake of the young creeper with shining teeth,</l>
<l rend="indent">twisting curls, and slender drum-like waist,</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti where, as the bees hum melodies,</l>
<l rend="indent">an elephant sleeps with its mate</l>
<l>On a beautiful hillock on a bed of flowers</l>
<l rend="indent">with the fragrance of the scented kino tree.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
